data.description: Sitting on half an acre, this home features an oversized living room with stunning, beamed ceilings and natural light pouring in through the windows. With plenty of room for hosting, the dining room leads into the delightful kitchen which is perfect for the home inspired chef. Other features of this home include spacious bedroom and closet sizes, an in-ground pool, and a two car garage on half acre lot. Call today to schedule a private showing!
